data.description: This charming 3 BR/2.5 BA beauty built in 1926 has so much character including the transom window above the front door and ornate staircase. Updates include granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances including a Professional Series side-by-side column refrigerator and freezer set, gas stove with pot filler, new flooring in the primary suite and much more.  Outside you'll find a detached 2 car garage with ADU perfect for rental income, out of town guests or even a home office space with full bath.  The oversized yard, including an additional city lot, is perfect for outdoor parties or simply relaxing by the fire pit. Just down the street, feel free to fill your water jugs from one of Little Rock's very own cold water natural springs.  So much history.  So much charm.  Come take a look at this beautiful home in revitalized downtown Little Rock. You’re going to love it here!
